$interpreted: Dylan: Still haven't found who made the coin sack?
Sione: My apologies. I've left no stone unturned, still to no avail...
Dylan: The grand anniversary is only days away. We must escort Her Highness back to the castle at once...
Sione: Understood. I'll find a way to expose Theodore's dirty little secret before the event, somehow.

Dylan: Take care. If the Sunshine Infantry and I weren't
under constant scrutiny, you wouldn't have to
run solo on this mission...
Sione: Jahan, that jerk....trying to make everyone's lives miserable again?
Dylan: Not this time. Although, he did send over one of those cranky cronies of his...
Cecil: The infantry's sense of discipline is disastrous!
Dylan: Security Officer Vincent, what's the matter?
Cecil: Someone's stolen my money! You Infantry imbeciles!
Sione: The Sunshine Infantry adheres to a strict moral code. We would never stoop so low!

Cecil: That's what she said, but it doesn't change the fact
that my coin sack is missing...EH?
Cecil: AGH! You-You wench, stole my coin sack you have!
Sione: This is what you're looking for?!
Cecil: And you think I wouldn't recognize my own property? What kind of fool do you take me for?!
Dylan: Officer Vincent, I'm sure there must be a misunderstanding...
Cecil: SILENCE! Allowing a subordinate to defy the law, I'll teach you!

Cecil: Get your dirty hands off me! I'm a Security Officer
under Colonel Augustinus! Dare lay a hand on me?
We'll see what our superiors have of this!
Sione: Colonel, are you injured?
Dylan: I'm fine, it's just...
Dylan: It all happened so fast, didn't mean to hit so hard. He won't let me off the hook that easily.
Sione: It's not the colonel's fault. He has always been especially rude to you because of his father...
Sunshine Soldier: ——Officer Vincent!
Sunshine Soldier: Eh? Where's Officer Vincent gone to?
Sione: Made his leave already. What of it?
Sunshine Soldier: I've found the officer's missing coin sack. It was right under his bed this whole time.
Dylan: Sione, bring it to me. I'd like to have a look.
Sione: Colonel, look at this.
Sione: Be it the fabric's texture or the sewing technique, they are perfectly identical in each and every way.
Dylan: ...This calls for an investigation. Sione, follow Cecil closely.
Sione: Understood.
